  "subject": "Chore: Update RTD config for ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Update RTD config for ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13\n\nRewrite .readthedocs.yaml from legacy build image format to the modern configuration using ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13. The legacy build image and Python 3.7 are both EOL. The ubuntu-20.04 build image will be removed by Read the Docs on June 1, 2026.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I80b5b53c57b2ae1546e8eedded1d727bf71661cc\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
